.............................................................................
.      CSTRTYR is the start of the financial year date
.      input  : XYEAR is financial year, XMON is the current month
.      output : IYEAR is offset year, IMON is the offset month
.
.                   08/10/1998  Glenn Berry      5.07 changes
.******************************************************************************
.
CALOFFST  OPEN      PATDRGA2,"patdrgaf"
          CALL      PATSTRYR                     * get start of year date
.
          UNPACK    CSTRTYR,CCENT,CYEAR,CMON,CDAY
          MOVE      CMON,IMON
          SUB       ONE,IMON
          MOVE      XMON,FORM2
          ADD       FORM2,IMON
.
          MOVE      XYEAR,IYEAR
          COMPARE   TEN3,IMON
          RETURN    IF LESS
.
.         In second half of financial year
.
          SUB       TEN2,IMON
          ADD       ONE,IYEAR
          RETURN
.
